k训练的模型在BrowseComp-Plus上取得了非常突出的成绩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q2xw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">与没有经过额外微调的Qwen3，和在传统QA数据集NQ、HotpotQA上训练的Search-R1模型相比，基于InfoSeek训练的模型在面对BrowseComp中的困难问题时，能够通过大幅提高搜索次数，以检索需要的信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89qngg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">其带来的助力也直接体现在了正确率的提升上，16.5%的准确率取得了当前开源模型的最佳效果，并且能够与Gemini、Sonnet 4.0等商业模型媲美。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505144385\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5654692931633836\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"863\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"863\" data-height=\"488\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"318\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=559564a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1zbcUVs0YrYUBtKVOcPrlwPgUvIlc60wuEOgv65ibMR41qeRIiasG6dndsIUutJJicNnR1k7DjicI49Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q1o0v\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:13px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5xxgh165l\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfm5xxgtnb3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图3. 各模型在BrowseComp-Plus基准上的表现，基于InfoSeek训练的3B模型的表现与当前的主流商业模型媲美</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q5hw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时，以HotpotQA等为代表的传统QA基准，通过高质量的多跳问题来评估模型进行多轮的推理和检索工具调用的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q15b5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">智源研究院使用InfoSeek数据所训练的模型，在多个多跳QA的benchmark上取得了非常亮眼的表现，进一步验证了InfoSeek的有效性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505144388\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5480880648899189\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"863\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"863\" data-height=\"473\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"308\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=deb1ea74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1zbcUVs0YrYUBtKVOcPrlwZ1AjYwPq3SpQI1ib08mK8uwYyXpfzKhuRTEcbRb7nibliawvzCjibxMKZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q1uzv\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfm5y5hfie7\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5y5h01raq\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图4. 各模型在多跳</span></span></span></span><span mpa-font-style=\"mfm5y5h01dwn\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">QA</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5y5h0sus\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">基准上的表现</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">总结</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q1o0b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据的质量决定了模型的高度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q24ot\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">InfoSeek为开源社区提供了高质量的训练数据和数据合成框架，为未来Deep Research的发展提供助力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q15si\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">智源研究院也会在这一领域持续深耕，未来期待与更多科研机构及产业伙伴合作，共同推动检索与人工智能的发展。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q21nk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">欢迎研究者与开发者关注并使用InfoSeek及后续系列工作，共建开放繁荣的开源生态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfm5t89q21nk\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfmf8zme5s9\"><span leaf=\"\">参考链接：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfmf8zmejsi\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/Lk123/InfoSeek\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/Lk123/InfoSeek</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfmf8zme182j\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/VectorSpaceLab/InfoSeek\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/VectorSpaceLab/InfoSeek</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: #888888;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfmf8zme8ao\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2509.00375\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2509.00375</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智源研究院开源首个面向深度研究的大规模数据合成框架 InfoSeek 及其数据集，通过“扩散-回溯”方法解决了大模型复杂推理数据短缺问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智源研究院开源首个面向深度研究的大规模数据合成框架 InfoSeek 及其数据集，通过“扩散-回溯”方法解决了大模型复杂推理数据短缺问题。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了智源研究院发布的 InfoSeek，这是首个面向“深度研究”场景的大规模开源数据集及其数据合成框架。针对大模型在处理需要高维度推理和多轮信息整合的深度研究任务时面临的高质量训练数据短板，智源团队将深度研究问题定义为层级约束满足问题（HCSP），并提出创新的“扩散-回溯”数据合成方法。该方法能大规模自动扩增高难度训练数据，已合成包含 5 万条样本的 InfoSeek 数据集。实验证明，基于 InfoSeek 训练的 3B 参数模型在 BrowseComp-Plus 基准上表现接近 Gemini 等商业模型，并在多跳 QA 任务上取得亮眼成绩，为推动大模型深度研究提供了坚实基础。相关数据集、代码和技术报告均已面向社区开放。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "智源提出将深度研究问题定义为层级约束满足问题（HCSP），为复杂 QA 任务提供了新视角。",
      "explanation": "这一数学等价关系揭示了深度研究任务的本质，有助于系统化地理解和构建需要多轮、多分支推理的复杂问题，超越传统单一/多跳 QA。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创新的“扩散-回溯”数据合成方法实现了深度研究训练数据的大规模自动扩增。",
      "explanation": "该方法能从根节点扩散构建 HCSP 树状结构，并通过回溯验证其正确性，有效解决了高质量、高难度训练数据稀缺的难题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "基于 InfoSeek 训练的小参数模型在复杂基准上表现优异，验证了数据集的有效性。",
      "explanation": "仅 3B 参数的模型在 BrowseComp-Plus 上接近顶尖商业模型，表明 InfoSeek 数据集能有效提升模型处理深度研究任务的能力，降低高性能模型训练门槛。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在大模型走向深度研究的道路上，高质量数据一直是最大短板。",
    "智源研究团队揭示了深度研究问题与层级约束满足问题（Hierarchical Constraint Satisfaction Problem）之间的数学等价关系，并由此提出了基于「扩散-回溯」过程的数据合成方法。",
    "利用上述方法，研究团队总计合成了包含 5 万条训练样本的数据集 InfoSeek，并据此训练出参数规模仅 3B 的智能体模型。",
    "在 BrowseComp-Plus 基准测试中，该模型取得了 16.5%的准确率，性能已接近 Gemini、Sonnet 4.0 等领先商业模型，充分验证了该方法在深度研究任务上的有效性与潜力。",
    "数据的质量决定了模型的高度。InfoSeek 为开源社区提供了高质量的训练数据和数据合成框架，为未来 Deep Research 的发展提供助力。"
  ],
